Security & Governance

Enterprise Security by Design

Move fast with AI, safely. Our platform is built with enterprise-grade security and governance from the ground up.

Infrastructure Security

SOC 2 Type II certified cloud infrastructure with 99.99% uptime SLA. Multi-region redundancy and automated failover.

  • End-to-end encryption
  • Multi-region backup
  • DDoS protection
  • Network isolation

Data Protection

Your data is encrypted at rest and in transit. We never use client data to train models without explicit consent.

  • AES-256 encryption
  • TLS 1.3 in transit
  • PII detection & masking
  • Data residency options

Access Control

Role-based access control with SSO integration. Complete audit trail of every action.

  • SSO/SAML integration
  • Role-based permissions
  • MFA enforcement
  • Session management

AI Governance

Human oversight built into every critical decision. Model versioning, testing, and approval workflows.

  • Human-in-the-loop
  • Model versioning
  • Output validation
  • Bias monitoring

AI Ethics

Responsible AI

We believe AI should augment human capabilities, not replace human judgment. Our governance framework ensures ethical, transparent AI deployment.

Human Oversight

Critical decisions always include human review. AI assists, humans decide.

Transparency

Clear explanations of how AI makes decisions. No black boxes in critical systems.

Continuous Monitoring

24/7 monitoring for model drift, bias, and performance degradation.
